-->N_Queens_Hill_Climbing.py consists of solving N-Queens Problem using Hill Climbing search Algorithm. 

Inputs for the project are to be given as follows:

1. This project is gonna ask the user to enter the initial state which is mentioned below :

Enter the value of N : 8

--After entering the value of N, ie.Number of Queens (8-Queens Problem)


2.The user should provide input for choosing the variants among Hill Climbing Search method :

Enter the variants of hill climbing search to use:
1 --> hill climbing classic; 
2 --> hill climbing with sideways moves; 
3 --> random restart without sideways moves
